6","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"公司本次募投项目产品需要通过客户性能测试\n与应用验证后才可对外出售并产生经济效益。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-03-CODES","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","locator":"page:5","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"中简科技碳纤维产品牌号 指\n\"ZT7\"表示为高于T700 级；\"ZT8\"表示为高于T800 级；\n\"ZT9\"表示为T1000/T1100 级；M 表示为\"石墨纤维\"；\"40，\n55，60\"表示为拉伸模量高低；\"3K、6K、12K\"指产品的规格","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-03-AEROSPACE","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","locator":"page:9","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"3）销售模式\n公司客户主要是国内大型航空航天企业集团，客户明确且集中度高，因此，公司采用直接销售的方式，销售产品全部\n为高性能碳纤维及碳纤维织物，且绝大部分用于航空航天领域，客户对公司产品各项性能参数指标通过定型、认证、评审\n通过后，进入最终用户认定的合格供方目录，由客户根据最终用户的需求，向公司下订单并签订 合同","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-03-REVENUE","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","locator":"page:11","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"分产品\n其中：碳纤维 551,519,993.79 67.88% 460,321,724.77 82.37% 19.81%\n碳纤维织物 260,368,545.87 32.05% 99,976,217.62 17.89% 160.43%","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-03-VOLUME","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","locator":"page:12","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"行业分类 项目 单位 2024 年 2023 年 同比增减\n新材料制造业\n销售量 KG 301,915.01 194,635.60 55.12%\n生产量 KG 306,163.72 244,927.17 25.00%\n库存量 KG 37,831.74 48,424.12 -21.87%\n相关数据同比发生变动 30%以上的原因说明\n适用 □不适用\n1、销售量的增加主要系本报告期内客户需求量增加所致。\n2、生产量增加主要系本报告期内三期项目部分产线已投产所致。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-03-DIRECTOR-DISSENT","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","locator":"page:2","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"姓名 职务 内容和原因\n温月芳 董事\n内容:项目建设情况、关联方认定及内控建设问题。\n原因:说明项目建设具体投资支出，合同签署；关联方认定缺乏依据；内控存在严重问题。\n本公司董事温月芳声明：因对项目建设情况、关联方认定及内控建设问题\n无法保证或持异议，无法保证本报告相关内容的真实性、准确性和完整性，请\n投资者注意投资风险。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-03-INTERNAL-CONTROL","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","locator":"page:39","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"内控审计报告意见类型 带强调事项段的无保留意见\n非财务报告是否存在重大缺陷 否\n会计师事务所是否出具非标准意见的内部控制审计报告\n是 □否\n中简科技 2024 年 3 月至 2024 年 8 月期间，存在未经董事会审议即开展委托理财情况；中简科技于 2024 年 10 月发生\n公章遗失情况。前述情况发生后，中简科技已修订和完善了相关管理制度以及执行，已于 2024 年 12 月31 日之前完成了上\n述内部控制缺陷的自查整改。\n尽管管理层完成整改并实施新控制措施，但由于整改后运行时间较短，其持续有效性需进一步观察。本段内容不影响\n对中简科技 2024 年 12 月31 日财务报告内部控制有效性的无保留意见。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-03-FS-AUDIT","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","locator":"page:62","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"审计意见类型 标准的无保留意见\n审计报告签署日期 2025 年04 月 14 日\n审计机构名称 天健会计师事务所（特殊普通合伙）\n审计报告文号 天健审〔2025〕5130 号\n注册会计师姓名 曹博、刘格娟\n审计报告正文\n中简科技股份有限公司全体股东：\n一、审计意见\n我们审计了中简科技股份有限公司（以下简称中简科技）财务报表，包括 2024 年12 月 31日的合并及母公司资产负债\n表，2024 年度的合并及母公司利润表、合并及母公司现金流量表、合并及母公司所有者权益变动表，以及相关财务报表附\n注。\n我们认为，后附的财务报表在所有重大方面按照企业会计准则的规定编制，公允反映了中简科技 2024 年12 月 31 日的\n合并及母公司财务状况，以及 2024 年度的合并及母公司经营成果和现金流量。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-03-AUDIT-SCOPE","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","locator":"page:63","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"四、其他信息\n中简科技管理层（以下简称管理层）对其他信息负责。其他信息包括年度报告中涵盖的信息，但不包括财务报表和我\n们的审计报告。\n我们对财务报表发表的审计意见不涵盖其他信息，我们也不对其他信息发表任何形式的鉴证结论。\n结合我们对财务报表的审计，我们的责任是阅读其他信息，在此过程中，考虑其他信息是否与财务报表或我们在审计\n过程中了解到的情况存在重大不一致或者似乎存在重大错报。\n基于我们已执行的工作，如果我们确定其他信息存在重大错报，我们应当报告该事实。在这方面，我们无任何事项需\n要报告。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-POL-01-POLICY-NODE","document_id":"DOC-221cf71790f1","locator":"block:13","locator_type":"doc_text_block","quote":"|3.5     |高性能纤维及制品和复合材料         |      |                        |\n|3.5.1   |高性能纤维及制品制造               |      |                        |\n|3.5.1.1 |玻璃纤维及制品制造                 |3061* |玻璃纤维及制品制造      |\n|3.5.1.2 |高性能碳纤维及制品制造             |2653* |合成纤维单（聚合）体制造|\n|        |                                   |3091* |石墨及碳素制品制造      |","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-POL-01-PRODUCTS","document_id":"DOC-221cf71790f1","locator":"block:103","locator_type":"doc_text_block","quote":"|3.5.1.2|高性能碳纤 |2653*|合成纤维单（ |聚丙烯腈原丝                     |\n|       |维及制品制 |     |聚合）体制造 |                                 |\n|       |造         |     |             |                                 |\n|       |           |3091*|石墨及碳素制 |高强碳纤维（拉伸强度≥4.9GPa且拉伸|\n|       |           |     |品制造       |模量≥230～260GPa）               |\n|       |           |     |             |高强中模碳纤维（拉伸强度≥4.5GPa且|\n|       |           |     |             |拉伸模量≥260～350GPa）           |\n|       |           |     |             |高模碳纤维（拉伸强度≥3～3.5GPa且 |\n|       |           |     |             |拉伸模量≥400GPa）                |\n|       |           |     |             |高强高模碳纤维（拉伸强度≥4.0GPa且|\n|       |           |     |             |拉伸模量≥350GPa）                |\n|       |           |     |             |碳纤维织物预制体（用于航空、航天 |\n|       |           |     |             |、风力发电等）                   |\n|       |           |     |             |碳纤维预制体（用于航空、航天、风 |\n|       |           |     |             |力发电等）                       |","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-POL-01-NANO-BRANCH","document_id":"DOC-221cf71790f1","locator":"block:15","locator_type":"doc_text_block","quote":"|3.6.3.3 |超材料制造                         |3254* |稀有稀土金属压延加工    |\n|3.6.4   |纳米材料制造                       |      |                        |\n|3.6.4.1 |碳基纳米材料制造                   |3091* |石墨及碳素制品制造      |\n|3.6.4.2 |无机纳米材料制造                   |2613* |无机盐制造              |","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-STD-06-SCOPE","document_id":"DOC-b6820b10938f","locator":"page:4","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"本文件界定了碳纤维\n、\n基体和助剂以及碳纤维复合材料所涉及的术语和定义\n。\n本文件适用于碳纤维及其复合材料\n。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-STD-06-DEFINITIONS","document_id":"DOC-b6820b10938f","locator":"page:4","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"３\n．\n１\n碳纤维\n犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n由有机纤维热解重组所制得的\n碳含量\n（\n６\n．\n５\n）\n超过\n９０％\n（\n质量分数\n）\n的\n纤维\n（\n３\n．\n２７\n）。\n３\n．\n２\n石墨纤维\n犵狉犪狆犺犻狋犲犳犻犫犲狉\n经\n石墨化\n（\n３\n．\n２３\n）\n处理\n，\n碳含量\n（\n６\n．\n５\n）\n不低于\n９９％\n（\n质量分数\n）\n的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。\n３\n．\n３\n碳纤维前驱体\n犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉狆狉犲犮狌狉狊狅狉\n碳纤维原丝\nｃａｒｂｏｎｆｉｂｅｒｐｒｅｃｕｒｓｏｒ\n经热解重组能转化为\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）\n的有机纤维\n。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-STD-06-ROUTES","document_id":"DOC-b6820b10938f","locator":"page:4","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"３\n．\n４\n聚丙烯腈基碳纤维\n犘犃犖犫犪狊犲犱犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n由丙烯腈聚合物\n（\nＰＡＮ\n）\n前驱体所制得的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。\n３\n．\n５\n粘胶基碳纤维\n狉犪狔狅狀犫犪狊犲犱犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n；\nｖｉｓｃｏｓｅｂａｓｅｄｃａｒｂｏｎｆｉｂｅｒ\n由粘胶前驱体所制得的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。\n３\n．\n６\n沥青基碳纤维\n狆犻狋犮犺犫犪狊犲犱犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n由各向异性或各向同性的沥青等富含稠环芳烃前驱体所制得的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。\n３\n．\n７\n木质素基碳纤维\n犾犻犵狀犻狀犫犪狊犲犱犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n由木质素前驱体所制得的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。\n３\n．\n８\n气相生长碳纤维\n狏犪狆狅狉犵狉狅狑狀犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n通过催化烃类在气相中分解生长而成的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-STD-06-USE-CATEGORIES","document_id":"DOC-b6820b10938f","locator":"page:5","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"３\n．\n１３\n宇航级碳纤维\n犪犲狉狅狊狆犪犮犲犵狉犪犱犲犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n性能及质量稳定性要求严格\n，\n可用于航空航天领域的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。\n３\n．\n１４\n工业级碳纤维\n犻狀犱狌狊狋狉犻犪犾犵狉犪犱犲犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n具有相对较低的生产成本\n，\n质量稳定性可以接受\n，\n适用于一般工业用途的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。\n３\n．\n１５\n回收碳纤维\n狉犲犮狔犮犾犲犱犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉\n经过对\n碳纤维复合材料\n（\n５\n．\n９\n）、\n预浸料\n（\n５\n．\n２２\n）\n以及\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）\n应用加工过程中产生的边角废料进行\n物理或\n（\n和\n）\n化学方法处理而得到的\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-STD-06-COMPOSITE","document_id":"DOC-b6820b10938f","locator":"page:16","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"５\n．\n９\n碳纤维复合材料\n犮犪狉犫狅狀犳犻犫犲狉犮狅犿狆狅狊犻狋犲\n以\n碳纤维\n（\n３\n．\n１\n）\n为\n增强体\n（\n３\n．\n９５\n）\n或功能体\n，\n以聚合物\n、\n金属\n、\n陶瓷\n、\n碳等为\n基体\n（\n４\n．\n８\n）\n的\n复合材料\n（\n５\n．\n１\n）。","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-02-WIND-REVENUE","document_id":"DOC-2e59fd4c4801","locator":"page:2","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"风电碳梁业务因传统主要客户订单量价齐跌、新开发\n客户虽开始导入量产但业务规模还有限，实现销售收入 4.26 亿元，较上年同期\n减少 35.54%","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-02-WIND-ADOPTION","document_id":"DOC-2e59fd4c4801","locator":"page:4","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"目前，风电领域已不断有新的主机厂开始采用\n风电碳梁开发风电叶片产品，公司持续努力开发的新客户也陆续开始转入批产，\n预期 2024 年公司风电碳梁业务可实现恢复性增长","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-COMP-02-WIND-ORDERS","document_id":"DOC-2e59fd4c4801","locator":"page:7","locator_type":"pdf_page","quote":"2021 年度碳梁业务实现营业收入 8.08 亿元，成为公司的重要业务支撑。但\n由于作为原材料的碳纤维价格上涨，下游主机厂市场拓展整体不及预期、市场竞\n争加剧等原因影响，客户维斯塔斯自 2022 年第四季度起订单调整，减少或者向\n境外转移订单，公司碳梁业务 2022 年度实现营业收入 6.62 亿元，2023 年度实\n现营业收入 4.26 亿元，相对2021 的业务峰值有大幅度下降，同时，伴随碳纤维\n原材料价格大幅上涨，业务的盈利能力大幅度波动。\n目前，随着新开发客户陆续导入量产，2024 年第一季度碳梁业务降幅明显\n收窄","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-APP-02-PURCHASE","document_id":"DOC-320677ee92c4","locator":"segment:158","locator_type":"html_text_segment","quote":"In another step forward for MHI Vestas’ industry-leading localisation plans in Taiwan, the company has confirmed a purchase agreement with Swancor to source several key blade manufacturing components locally. This contract strengthens Swancor’s presence in the offshore wind sector, and will deliver substantial value to the Taiwanese economy through knowledge sharing, jobs and direct investment.","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-APP-02-CARBON-COMPONENTS","document_id":"DOC-320677ee92c4","locator":"segment:159","locator_type":"html_text_segment","quote":"The scope of the Swancor contract goes substantially beyond local requirements for blade materials and covers a significant percentage of the direct materials value of overall blade manufacturing (including pultruded carbon plates, resin, and bonding glue).","status":"reviewed"},{"citation_id":"CIT-CF-APP-02-PROJECT","document_id":"DOC-320677ee92c4","locator":"segment:168","locator_type":"html_text_segment","quote":"“Since 2018 we have been working closely with MHI Vestas on localisation for blades. Apart from resin, a required item by Taiwan’s localisation policy, the contract between Swancor and MHI Vestas also additionally includes the supply of carbon tow, carbon pultrusion, and bonding glue. The active effort from MHI Vestas and CIP greatly enhances the value of a local blade supply chain. Now with Tien Li and Swancor, the right supply set up for blade manufacturing is in place. CIP is looking forward to receiving the first local fabricated offshore blade in Taiwan for its Changfang and Xidao projects.”","status":"reviewed"}],"claim_evidence":[{"claim_id":"CLM-ISIC4-CORR-3830","evidence_id":"EVD-ISIC4-CORR-3830","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-PAN-OXIDATION-CHAIN","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-PAN-OXIDATION-CHAIN","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-OXIDATION-EQUIPMENT","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-OXIDATION-EQUIPMENT","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-EQUIVALENCE-202109","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-EQUIVALENCE-202109","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-VALIDATION-RISK","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-VALIDATION-RISK","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-CODES","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-03-CODES","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-AEROSPACE","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-03-AEROSPACE","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-REVENUE","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-03-REVENUE","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-VOLUME","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-03-VOLUME","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-DIRECTOR-DISSENT","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-03-DIRECTOR-DISSENT","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-INTERNAL-CONTROL","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-03-INTERNAL-CONTROL","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-FS-AUDIT","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-03-FS-AUDIT","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-AUDIT-SCOPE","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-03-AUDIT-SCOPE","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLAIM-CF-POL-01-POLICY-NODE","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-POL-01-POLICY-NODE","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLAIM-CF-POL-01-PRODUCTS","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-POL-01-PRODUCTS","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLAIM-CF-POL-01-NANO-BRANCH","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-POL-01-NANO-BRANCH","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-SCOPE","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-STD-06-SCOPE","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-DEFINITIONS","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-STD-06-DEFINITIONS","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-ROUTES","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-STD-06-ROUTES","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-USE-CATEGORIES","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-STD-06-USE-CATEGORIES","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-COMPOSITE","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-STD-06-COMPOSITE","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-02-WIND-REVENUE","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-02-WIND-REVENUE","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-02-WIND-ADOPTION","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-02-WIND-ADOPTION","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-02-WIND-ORDERS","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-COMP-02-WIND-ORDERS","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-APP-02-PURCHASE","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-APP-02-PURCHASE","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-APP-02-CARBON-COMPONENTS","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-APP-02-CARBON-COMPONENTS","support_type":"supports"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-APP-02-PROJECT","evidence_id":"EVD-CF-APP-02-PROJECT","support_type":"supports"}],"claims":[{"claim_id":"CLM-ISIC4-CORR-3830","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"ISIC Rev.4数据库版本对3830类第一项排除说明作了文字修订，删除了metal一词。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-PAN-OXIDATION-CHAIN","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技披露，其相关碳纤维生产工艺以丙烯腈为原材料，经聚合、纺丝形成碳纤维原丝，再经氧化碳化形成高性能碳纤维。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-OXIDATION-EQUIPMENT","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技披露的募投项目设备清单包含氧化装置、碳化、表面处理和上浆系统。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-EQUIVALENCE-202109","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技披露，其前次募投项目千吨线于2021年9月底通过客户A的等同性验证评审。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-VALIDATION-RISK","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技披露，相关募投产品需要通过客户性能测试与应用验证后才可销售并产生经济效益，验证周期与结果存在不确定性。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-CODES","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技2024年年报将ZT7、ZT8、ZT9、M及40/55/60、3K/6K/12K分别解释为公司碳纤维产品的级别、模量和规格编码。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-AEROSPACE","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技披露其直接销售的高性能碳纤维及碳纤维织物绝大部分用于航空航天领域，相关性能指标经定型、认证、评审后进入最终用户认定的合格供方目录。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-REVENUE","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技2024年年报分产品披露碳纤维营业收入551,519,993.79元、碳纤维织物营业收入260,368,545.87元。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-VOLUME","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技2024年年报以新材料制造业行业合并口径披露销售量301,915.01KG、生产量306,163.72KG和库存量37,831.74KG；该口径不能拆分为单一碳纤维产品数量。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-DIRECTOR-DISSENT","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技2024年年报披露，一名董事对项目建设情况、关联方认定及内控建设问题无法保证或持异议，并提示投资风险。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-INTERNAL-CONTROL","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"中简科技2024年内部控制审计意见为带强调事项段的无保留意见，强调未经董事会审议开展委托理财、公章遗失以及整改后持续有效性仍需观察。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-FS-AUDIT","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"天健会计师事务所对中简科技2024年度财务报表出具标准的无保留意见。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-03-AUDIT-SCOPE","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"审计报告明确，财务报表审计意见不涵盖年度报告中的其他信息，也不对其他信息发表任何形式的鉴证结论。"},{"claim_id":"CLAIM-CF-POL-01-POLICY-NODE","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"《战略性新兴产业分类（2018）》将“高性能碳纤维及制品制造”置于3.5.1“高性能纤维及制品制造”下，并以带星号的2653和3091经济活动代码对应，表示部分活动口径。"},{"claim_id":"CLAIM-CF-POL-01-PRODUCTS","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"该政策分类在3.5.1.2下列示聚丙烯腈原丝、多类高性能碳纤维、碳纤维织物预制体和碳纤维预制体等重点产品。"},{"claim_id":"CLAIM-CF-POL-01-NANO-BRANCH","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"该政策分类将“纳米材料制造”列为3.6.4独立分支，与3.5.1.2高性能碳纤维及制品制造不是同一分类节点。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-SCOPE","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"GB/T 40724-2021界定碳纤维、基体和助剂及碳纤维复合材料相关术语和定义，适用于碳纤维及其复合材料。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-DEFINITIONS","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"GB/T 40724-2021分别定义碳纤维、石墨纤维和碳纤维前驱体，三者不是同一对象。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-ROUTES","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"GB/T 40724-2021分别列示聚丙烯腈基、粘胶基、沥青基、木质素基和气相生长碳纤维术语。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-USE-CATEGORIES","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"GB/T 40724-2021定义宇航级碳纤维、工业级碳纤维和回收碳纤维。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-STD-06-COMPOSITE","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"verified","statement":"GB/T 40724-2021将碳纤维复合材料定义为以碳纤维为增强体或功能体，并以聚合物、金属、陶瓷、碳等为基体的复合材料。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-02-WIND-REVENUE","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"公司披露，2023年风电碳梁业务因传统主要客户订单量价齐跌，销售收入为4.26亿元，同比减少35.54%。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-02-WIND-ADOPTION","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"公司披露，风电领域已有新的主机厂开始采用风电碳梁开发风电叶片产品，新客户陆续转入批产。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-COMP-02-WIND-ORDERS","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"公司披露，维斯塔斯订单自2022年第四季度起调整，减少或向境外转移；碳梁业务收入由2021年的8.08亿元降至2023年的4.26亿元。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-APP-02-PURCHASE","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"MHI Vestas官方公告披露，其与Swancor确认采购协议，以采购本地叶片制造的关键部件。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-APP-02-CARBON-COMPONENTS","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"MHI Vestas官方公告披露，Swancor采购范围包括拉挤碳板、碳纤维丝束和碳拉挤材料。"},{"claim_id":"CLM-CF-APP-02-PROJECT","claim_type":"reported_fact","review_status":"reviewed","source_status":"reported","statement":"MHI Vestas官方公告披露，该采购关系对应CIP的Changfang和Xidao项目，项目方期待接收首批本地制造海上风电叶片。"}],"documents":[{"accessed_date":"2026-07-16","document_id":"DOC-70ab10969125","document_type":"txt","language":"en","license_status":"official_public_reference","official_url":"https://unstats.un.org/unsd/classifications/Econ/Download/In%20Text/ISIC_Rev_4_english_database.zip","published_date":"","review_status":"reviewed","source_id":"SRC-005","title":"ISIC Rev.4数据库官方修订说明"},{"accessed_date":"2026-07-18","document_id":"DOC-1d8bdf89b784","document_type":"pdf","language":"zh","license_status":"official_public_reference","official_url":"https://static.cninfo.com.cn/finalpage/2021-11-26/1211706689.PDF","published_date":"2021-11-26","review_status":"reviewed","source_id":"CF-COMP-04","title":"向特定对象发行审核问询函回复（修订版）"},{"accessed_date":"2026-07-18","document_id":"DOC-d0dd6c236f45","document_type":"pdf","language":"zh","license_status":"official_public_reference","official_url":"https://static.cninfo.com.cn/finalpage/2025-04-15/1223097527.PDF","published_date":"2025-04-15","review_status":"reviewed","source_id":"CF-COMP-03","title":"2024年年度报告"},{"accessed_date":"2026-07-18","document_id":"DOC-221cf71790f1","document_type":"doc","language":"zh","license_status":"official_public_reference","official_url":"https://www.stats.gov.cn/xxgk/tjbz/gjtjbz/202008/P020241210500130072993.doc","published_date":"2018-11-07","review_status":"reviewed","source_id":"CF-POL-01","title":"战略性新兴产业分类（2018）"},{"accessed_date":"2026-07-19","document_id":"DOC-b6820b10938f","document_type":"pdf","language":"zh","license_status":"official_public_reference","official_url":"https://openstd.samr.gov.cn/bzgk/std/newGbInfo?hcno=6FCA96E97DD486AF201B139DD0CF8F39","published_date":"2021-10-11","review_status":"reviewed","source_id":"CF-STD-06","title":"GB/T 40724-2021 碳纤维及其复合材料术语"},{"accessed_date":"2026-07-19","document_id":"DOC-2e59fd4c4801","document_type":"pdf","language":"zh","licen